{"story":{"group_1":[{"bgm":"bgm03_story12","nameNarration":"电视","narration":"「市议会议员美国久臣@在家中上吊自杀」","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21083.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"「美国议员疑似有贪污渎职行为……」"},{"bg":"bg_adv_21021.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":400101,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":800100,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"美国织莉子","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"来了！@是美国同学！","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"blackPromist"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":800200,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"textRight":"难以置信！@明明发生了那种事……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":800200}],"textRight":"要是我，肯定会羞得@根本没脸来学校。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":800100,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"textRight":"喂，她会听见的啦！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":800200,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"textRight":"她……@可是罪犯的女儿啊！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":400101,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"…………"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story08","chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":400101},{"effect":"fadeout","id":800200}],"nameNarration":"美国织莉子","narration":"对大家来说，我不是“美国织莉子”@只是“美国议员”……@“美国久臣的女儿”","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21172.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"大家只会透过父亲来认识我@只把我视为父亲的一部分@既然如此……"},{"bg":"bg_adv_21083.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":400101,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"nameCenter":"美国织莉子","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"我……@是为什么而活着的呢？","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":400101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textCenter":"（我已经搞不懂……@自己活着有什么意义了……）"},{"bg":"bg_adv_21071.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":400101,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"美国织莉子","textCenter":"——！！","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":400101}],"textCenter":"是、梦啊……[chara:400101:cheek_0:face_mtn_ex_030.exp.json]"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story08","narration":"我明明成为了魔法少女@知道了自己活着的意义……@但现在，我还是会做那种梦","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21171.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"虽然我能理解自己活着的意义@但同时，@我也希望……"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":400101,"motion":1}],"nameCenter":"美国织莉子","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"有人能认同“美国织莉子”还活着……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":400101,"motion":300}],"textCenter":"……？@这个香气是……"},{"bg":"bg_adv_21081.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":400101,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"美国织莉子","textRight":"纪里香，@你来了啊。","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":400201,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"吴纪里香","textLeft":"织莉子！@你醒了吗？织莉子！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":400101}],"textRight":"这红茶……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":400201,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"是织莉子说过的@大吉岭！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":400201}],"textLeft":"我起了个大早，@去神滨买来的！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":400101,"motion":300}],"textRight":"你专程去……@不用这么费心的呀。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":400201,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"因为织莉子想喝的，@其实是这种红茶吧？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":400201,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"要是没能@实现你的愿望，"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":400201,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"我会过意不去的。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":400101,"motion":0}],"textRight":"纪里香……"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story07","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":400201,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"织莉子？@我没弄错吧？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"effect":"emotion_sad_0","face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":400201,"motion":0}],"se":"7224_fall_into","textLeft":"是这种红茶没错吧？@你不开心吗？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":400101,"motion":200}],"textRight":"呵呵，别担心。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":400101,"motion":0}],"textRight":"我想喝的@就是这种红茶哦。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":400101}],"textRight":"谢谢你，纪里香。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":400201}],"textLeft":"……！@[chara:400201:cheek_1:face_mtn_ex_012.exp.json:motion_100]不用跟我道谢啦！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":400201}],"textLeft":"只要是为了织莉子，"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":400201,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"无论何时，无论何地，@无论多少次，我都可以出发！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":400101}],"textRight":"但是……今后你可不能不经过我同意，@就去太远的地方。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":400101,"motion":300}],"textRight":"要是你有什么万一，@我会为难的。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":400201,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"嗯！我知道了！@我知道了，织莉子！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":400201}],"textLeft":"来！趁茶还没凉，@我们来个茶歇吧！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":400101,"motion":200}],"textRight":"嗯，好啊。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":400101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textRight":"（会认同我的人……）"},{"narration":"会将我视为“美国织莉子”的人……@就在这里","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21171.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":400101,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4001_00_05","textHome":"如果没有你，我估计早就坏掉了吧。"}],"nameCenter":"美国织莉子","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"如果没有你在身边，@我恐怕早就已经崩溃了吧。","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":400101,"motion":1}]},{"chara":[{"id":400101}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}